### Arabic

وَإِن نَّشَأْ نُغْرِقْهُمْ فَلَا صَرِيخَ لَهُمْ وَلَا هُمْ يُنقَذُونَ

### English

If We willed, We could drown them: then no one would respond to their cries, nor would they be rescued—